name: GoDino
description:
This game is a game to collect coins, if the player catches a black bomb, there will be a reduction in coins. but if the player touches the fiery bomb then the game will be restarted.

space : For jump

button 'A' : For retreat

button 'D': For forward

or you can use cursor control keys to control the player

You must see the video thailer before you play game
